StudyInfo.StudyNameEntrez: Neurobiology of Postraumatic Stress Disorder Dysfunction and Recovery following Cognitive Processing Therapy (Ressler)

Person.Organization: COLUMBIA UNIVERSITY HEALTH SCIENCESBOSTON UNIVERSITY MEDICAL CAMPUSHARVARD SCHOOL OF PUBLIC HEALTH

Policy.acknowledgement_statement: Samples used for data analysis were provided by a collaboration of about 8 groups, working together through the Psychiatric Genomics Consortium PTSD. Support for these samples include support from NIMH including [R01 MH106595-01A1, Cohens Veterans Science], and the Stanley Center for Psychiatric Research.
